{"tid":2164721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"寫字樓價格顯著下跌，金管局希望大家去救市","createTime":"2020-08-19T10:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T13:35:08.000Z","uid":48040,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7a96c65ccb72e6abe4816db50e263f9a5d30b7dc","tid":2164721,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"金管局放寬非住宅物業按揭貸款的逆周期宏觀審慎監管措施，非住宅物業適用按揭成數上限上調10個百分點，一般個案的上限由4成上調至5成，明日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n金管局總裁余偉文表示，新型冠狀病毒疫情對本港經濟造成重大壓力，雖然住宅物業市場維持平穩，但非住宅物業包括寫字樓、分層工廠大廈及零售業樓宇價格及成交量均顯著調整。<span class=\"orange\">鑑於疫情及持續升溫的地緣政治緊張局勢，將繼續影響營商信心，非住宅物業市場預期持續受壓</span>。考慮到非住宅物業價格走勢、交投量、經濟基調和外圍環境等因素，金管局認為現時適合放寬有關措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544687-20200819.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544687-20200819.htm&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=d2e266e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544687-20200819.htm&h=f125df9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544687-20200819.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e02ec9e4ba3a036d2ad5b480b1cb79a8cd49256","tid":2164721,"uid":73972,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"On9，經濟不穩，失業機會大仲叫人借多d錢"},{"pid":"219ccadab6463233b2bbef7de70f9eb546e90295","tid":2164721,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1e02ec9e4ba3a036d2ad5b480b1cb79a8cd49256","tid":2164721,"uid":73972,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"On9，經濟不穩，失業機會大仲叫人借多d錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bc5df5005756d02aed6d7e947f693b29a5e927","tid":2164721,"uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"「地緣政治」，根本就係人禍。"},{"pid":"cc02be34ed444b3273d